'''''Big Bang''''' is a 1988 video game published by [[Zortech]].

==Gameplay==
''Big Bang'' is a [[stock market simulator]] and features 100 companies on the stock exchange.<ref name="gi11"/>

==Publication history==
''Big Bang'' was released in August 1988, the first game from software publisher Zortech.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/97934699/the-guardian/|title=Clipped from the Guardian|newspaper=The Guardian|date=4 August 1988|page=25}}</ref>

